{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-001", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [1]", "text_original": "禹別九州隨山濬川。任土作《貢》。", "text_normalized": "禹別九州隨山濬川。任土作《貢》。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-002", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [2]", "text_original": "禹敷土，隨山刊木，奠高山大川。", "text_normalized": "禹敷土，隨山刊木，奠高山大川。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-003", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [3]", "text_original": "冀州：既載壺口，治梁及岐。既修太原，至于岳陽；覃懷厎績，至于衡漳。厥土惟白壤，厥賦惟上上錯，厥田惟中中。恆、衛既從，大陸既作。島夷皮服，夾右碣石入于河。", "text_normalized": "冀州：既載壺口，治梁及岐。既修太原，至于岳陽；覃懷厎績，至于衡漳。厥土惟白壤，厥賦惟上上錯，厥田惟中中。恆、衛既從，大陸既作。島夷皮服，夾右碣石入于河。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-004", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 4, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [4]", "text_original": "濟河惟兗州。九河既道，雷夏既澤，灉、沮會同。桑土既蠶，是降丘宅土。厥土黑墳，厥草惟繇，厥木惟條。厥田惟中下，厥賦貞，作十有三載乃同。厥貢漆絲，厥篚織文。浮于濟、漯，達于河。", "text_normalized": "濟河惟兗州。九河既道，雷夏既澤，灉、沮會同。桑土既蠶，是降丘宅土。厥土黑墳，厥草惟繇，厥木惟條。厥田惟中下，厥賦貞，作十有三載乃同。厥貢漆絲，厥篚織文。浮于濟、漯，達于河。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-005", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 5, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [5]", "text_original": "海岱惟青州。嵎夷既略，濰、淄其道。厥土白墳，海濱廣斥。厥田惟上下，厥賦中上。厥貢鹽絺，海物惟錯。岱畎絲、枲、鉛、松、怪石。萊夷作牧。厥篚檿絲。浮于汶，達于濟。", "text_normalized": "海岱惟青州。嵎夷既略，濰、淄其道。厥土白墳，海濱廣斥。厥田惟上下，厥賦中上。厥貢鹽絺，海物惟錯。岱畎絲、枲、鉛、松、怪石。萊夷作牧。厥篚檿絲。浮于汶，達于濟。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-006", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 6, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [6]", "text_original": "海、岱及淮惟徐州。淮、沂其乂，蒙、羽其藝，大野既豬，東原厎平。厥土赤埴墳，草木漸包。厥田惟上中，厥賦中中。厥貢惟土五色，羽畎夏翟，嶧陽孤桐，泗濱浮磬，淮夷蠙珠暨魚。厥篚玄纖、縞。浮于淮、泗，達于河。", "text_normalized": "海、岱及淮惟徐州。淮、沂其乂，蒙、羽其藝，大野既豬，東原厎平。厥土赤埴墳，草木漸包。厥田惟上中，厥賦中中。厥貢惟土五色，羽畎夏翟，嶧陽孤桐，泗濱浮磬，淮夷蠙珠暨魚。厥篚玄纖、縞。浮于淮、泗，達于河。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-007", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 7, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [7]", "text_original": "淮海惟揚州。彭蠡既豬，陽鳥攸居。三江既入，震澤厎定。篠、簜既敷，厥草惟夭，厥木惟喬。厥土惟塗泥。厥田唯下下，厥賦下上，上錯。厥貢惟金三品，瑤、琨、篠、簜、齒、革、羽、毛惟木。鳥夷卉服。厥篚織貝，厥包橘柚，錫貢。沿于江、海，達于淮、泗。", "text_normalized": "淮海惟揚州。彭蠡既豬，陽鳥攸居。三江既入，震澤厎定。篠、簜既敷，厥草惟夭，厥木惟喬。厥土惟塗泥。厥田唯下下，厥賦下上，上錯。厥貢惟金三品，瑤、琨、篠、簜、齒、革、羽、毛惟木。鳥夷卉服。厥篚織貝，厥包橘柚，錫貢。沿于江、海，達于淮、泗。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-008", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 8, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [8]", "text_original": "荊及衡陽惟荊州。江、漢朝宗于海，九江孔殷，沱、潛既道，雲土、夢作乂。厥土惟塗泥，厥田惟下中，厥賦上下。厥貢羽、毛、齒、革惟金三品，杶、榦、栝、柏，礪、砥、砮、丹，惟菌、簵、楛；三邦厎貢厥名。包匭菁茅，厥篚玄纁璣組，九江納錫大龜。浮于江、沱、潛、漢，逾于洛，至于南河。", "text_normalized": "荊及衡陽惟荊州。江、漢朝宗于海，九江孔殷，沱、潛既道，雲土、夢作乂。厥土惟塗泥，厥田惟下中，厥賦上下。厥貢羽、毛、齒、革惟金三品，杶、榦、栝、柏，礪、砥、砮、丹，惟菌、簵、楛；三邦厎貢厥名。包匭菁茅，厥篚玄纁璣組，九江納錫大龜。浮于江、沱、潛、漢，逾于洛，至于南河。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-009", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 9, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [9]", "text_original": "荊河惟豫州。伊、洛、瀍、澗既入于河，滎波既豬。導菏澤，被孟豬。厥土惟壤，下土墳壚。厥田惟中上，厥賦錯上中。厥貢漆、枲，絺、紵，厥篚纖、纊，錫貢磬錯。浮于洛，達于河。", "text_normalized": "荊河惟豫州。伊、洛、瀍、澗既入于河，滎波既豬。導菏澤，被孟豬。厥土惟壤，下土墳壚。厥田惟中上，厥賦錯上中。厥貢漆、枲，絺、紵，厥篚纖、纊，錫貢磬錯。浮于洛，達于河。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-010", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 10, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [10]", "text_original": "華陽、黑水惟梁州。岷、嶓既藝，沱、潛既道。蔡、蒙旅平，和夷厎績。厥土青黎，厥田惟下上，厥賦下中，三錯。厥貢璆、鐵、銀、鏤、砮磬、熊、羆、狐、狸、織皮，西傾因桓是來，浮于潛，逾于沔，入于渭，亂于河。", "text_normalized": "華陽、黑水惟梁州。岷、嶓既藝，沱、潛既道。蔡、蒙旅平，和夷厎績。厥土青黎，厥田惟下上，厥賦下中，三錯。厥貢璆、鐵、銀、鏤、砮磬、熊、羆、狐、狸、織皮，西傾因桓是來，浮于潛，逾于沔，入于渭，亂于河。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-011", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 11, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [11]", "text_original": "黑水、西河惟雍州。弱水既西，涇屬渭汭，漆沮既從，灃水攸同。荊、岐既旅，終南、惇物，至于鳥鼠。原隰厎績，至于豬野。三危既宅，三苗丕敘。厥土惟黃壤，厥田惟上上，厥賦中下。厥貢惟球、琳、琅玕。浮于積石，至于龍門、西河，會于渭汭。織皮崐崘、析支、渠搜，西戎即敘。", "text_normalized": "黑水、西河惟雍州。弱水既西，涇屬渭汭，漆沮既從，灃水攸同。荊、岐既旅，終南、惇物，至于鳥鼠。原隰厎績，至于豬野。三危既宅，三苗丕敘。厥土惟黃壤，厥田惟上上，厥賦中下。厥貢惟球、琳、琅玕。浮于積石，至于龍門、西河，會于渭汭。織皮崐崘、析支、渠搜，西戎即敘。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-012", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 12, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [12]", "text_original": "導岍及岐，至于荊山，逾于河；壺口、雷首至于太岳；厎柱、析城至于王屋；太行、恆山至于碣石，入于海。", "text_normalized": "導岍及岐，至于荊山，逾于河；壺口、雷首至于太岳；厎柱、析城至于王屋；太行、恆山至于碣石，入于海。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-013", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 13, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [13]", "text_original": "西傾、朱圉、鳥鼠至于太華；熊耳、外方、桐柏至于陪尾。", "text_normalized": "西傾、朱圉、鳥鼠至于太華；熊耳、外方、桐柏至于陪尾。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-014", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 14, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [14]", "text_original": "導嶓冢，至于荊山；內方，至于大別。", "text_normalized": "導嶓冢，至于荊山；內方，至于大別。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-015", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 15, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [15]", "text_original": "岷山之陽，至于衡山，過九江，至于敷淺原。", "text_normalized": "岷山之陽，至于衡山，過九江，至于敷淺原。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-016", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 16, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [16]", "text_original": "導弱水，至于合黎，餘波入于流沙。", "text_normalized": "導弱水，至于合黎，餘波入于流沙。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-017", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 17, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [17]", "text_original": "導黑水，至于三危，入于南海。", "text_normalized": "導黑水，至于三危，入于南海。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-018", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 18, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [18]", "text_original": "導河、積石，至于龍門；南至于華陰，東至于厎柱，又東至于孟津，東過洛汭，至于大伾；北過降水，至于大陸；又北，播為九河，同為逆河，入于海。", "text_normalized": "導河、積石，至于龍門；南至于華陰，東至于厎柱，又東至于孟津，東過洛汭，至于大伾；北過降水，至于大陸；又北，播為九河，同為逆河，入于海。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-019", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 19, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [19]", "text_original": "嶓冢導漾，東流為漢，又東，為滄浪之水，過三澨，至于大別，南入于江。東，匯澤為彭蠡，東，為北江，入于海。", "text_normalized": "嶓冢導漾，東流為漢，又東，為滄浪之水，過三澨，至于大別，南入于江。東，匯澤為彭蠡，東，為北江，入于海。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-020", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 20, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [20]", "text_original": "岷山導江，東別為沱，又東至于澧；過九江，至于東陵，東迆北，會于匯；東為中江，入于海。", "text_normalized": "岷山導江，東別為沱，又東至于澧；過九江，至于東陵，東迆北，會于匯；東為中江，入于海。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-021", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 21, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [21]", "text_original": "導沇水，東流為濟，入于河，溢為滎；東出于陶丘北，又東至于菏，又東北，會于汶，又北，東入于海。", "text_normalized": "導沇水，東流為濟，入于河，溢為滎；東出于陶丘北，又東至于菏，又東北，會于汶，又北，東入于海。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-022", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 22, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [22]", "text_original": "導淮自桐柏，東會于泗、沂，東入于海。", "text_normalized": "導淮自桐柏，東會于泗、沂，東入于海。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-023", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 23, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [23]", "text_original": "導渭自鳥鼠同穴，東會于灃，又東會于涇，又東過漆沮，入于河。", "text_normalized": "導渭自鳥鼠同穴，東會于灃，又東會于涇，又東過漆沮，入于河。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-024", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 24, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [24]", "text_original": "導洛自熊耳，東北，會于澗、瀍；又東，會于伊，又東北，入于河。", "text_normalized": "導洛自熊耳，東北，會于澗、瀍；又東，會于伊，又東北，入于河。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-025", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 25, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [25]", "text_original": "九州攸同，四隩既宅，九山刊旅，九川滌源，九澤既陂，四海會同。六府孔修，庶土交正，厎慎財賦，咸則三壤成賦。中邦錫土、姓，祗台德先，不距朕行。", "text_normalized": "九州攸同，四隩既宅，九山刊旅，九川滌源，九澤既陂，四海會同。六府孔修，庶土交正，厎慎財賦，咸則三壤成賦。中邦錫土、姓，祗台德先，不距朕行。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-026", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 26, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [26]", "text_original": "五百里甸服：百里賦納總，二百里納銍，三百里納秸服，四百里粟，五百里米。", "text_normalized": "五百里甸服：百里賦納總，二百里納銍，三百里納秸服，四百里粟，五百里米。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-027", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 27, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [27]", "text_original": "五百里侯服：百里采，二百里男邦，三百里諸侯。", "text_normalized": "五百里侯服：百里采，二百里男邦，三百里諸侯。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-028", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 28, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [28]", "text_original": "五百里綏服：三百里揆文教，二百里奮武衛。", "text_normalized": "五百里綏服：三百里揆文教，二百里奮武衛。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-029", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 29, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [29]", "text_original": "五百里要服：三百里夷，二百里蔡。", "text_normalized": "五百里要服：三百里夷，二百里蔡。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-030", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 30, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [30]", "text_original": "五百里荒服：三百里蠻，二百里流。", "text_normalized": "五百里荒服：三百里蠻，二百里流。", "notes": ""}
{"segment_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3__segment-031", "work_id": "shangshu", "section_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu", "source_id": "shangshu-007-xia-shu-tribute-of-yu__chinesenotes-shangshu-zh-1f6b1d3", "segment_type": "block", "segment_order": 31, "canonical_ref": "尚書·夏書 禹貢 [31]", "text_original": "東漸于海，西被于流沙，朔南暨聲教訖于四海。禹錫玄圭，告厥成功。", "text_normalized": "東漸于海，西被于流沙，朔南暨聲教訖于四海。禹錫玄圭，告厥成功。", "notes": ""}
